queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.142.120.95', 'user_list', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/user_list?gender_type=All&search_radius=74', '2020-11-18 10:17:42', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'user_list-1605694662.json')

SELECT `m`.`vVideoThumbnail` AS `video_thumbnail`,`u`.`iUserId` AS `user_id`,(concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName)) AS user_name,`u`.`vFirstName` AS `u_first_name`,`u`.`vLastName` AS `u_last_name`,`u`.`vEmail` AS `u_email`,`u`.`vMobileNo` AS `u_mobile_no`,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `user_image`,`u`.`vDescription` AS `description`,`u`.`dDob` AS `u_dob`,`u`.`tAddress` AS `u_address`,`u`.`vCity` AS `city`,`u`.`dLatitude` AS `u_latitude`,`u`.`dLongitude` AS `u_longitude`,`u`.`iStateId` AS `u_state_id`,`u`.`vStateName` AS `state`,`u`.`vZipCode` AS `u_zip_code`,`u`.`iAge` AS `age`,`u`.`eStatus` AS `u_status`,GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT  i.vBreedsName SEPARATOR ',') AS breed_name,GROUP_CONCAT( DISTINCT `m`.`iMediaId` SEPARATOR ',')  AS media_id,('') AS connection_type_by_logged_user,('') AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,`p`.`iPetId` AS `pet_id`,`p`.`vPetName` AS `pet_name`,`p`.`vBreed` AS `breed`,`p`.`vPetAge` AS `pet_age`,`p`.`vPetCategory` AS `pet_category`,`p`.`vPetDescription` AS `pet_description`,`p`.`vAKCRegistered` AS `akc_registered` FROM `users` AS `u` LEFT JOIN `user_breed` AS `ui` ON `ui`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `breeds` AS `i` ON `i`.`iBreedsId` = `ui`.`iBreedsId` LEFT JOIN `user_media` AS `m` ON `m`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `pet` AS `p` ON `p`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` WHERE FLOOR(             3959 * acos (               cos ( radians(34.02324310) )               * cos( radians( u.dLatitude ) )               * cos( radians( u.dLongitude ) - radians(-84.36155550))               + sin ( radians(34.02324310) )               * sin( radians( u.dLatitude ))             )) <= '74' AND u.iUserId not in (SELECT DISTINCT(u.iUserId) AS user_id                 FROM users AS u                 LEFT JOIN user_connections AS uc ON uc.iConnectionUserId = u.iUserId                  LEFT JOIN user_connections AS ub ON ub.iUserId = u.iUserId                  WHERE u.eStatus = 'Active' AND (`uc`.`iUserId` = '1' OR (`ub`.`eConnectionResult` = 'Block' AND ub.iConnectionUserId = '1'))) AND `u`.`iUserId` <> '1' AND `u`.`eStatus` = 'Active' GROUP BY `user_id`

SELECT '' AS connection_type,                          (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=1 AND  iConnectionUserId = 4) AS connection_type_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=1 AND  iConnectionUserId = 4) AS connection_result_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=4 AND  iConnectionUserId = 1) AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=4 AND  iConnectionUserId = 1) AS connection_result_by_receiver_user                                                  FROM user_connections LIMIT 1

SELECT `m`.`iMediaId` AS `media_id`,`m`.`iUserId` AS `m_user_id`,`m`.`vMediaType` AS `media_type`,`m`.`vVideoThumbnail` AS `video_thumbnail`,`m`.`vMediaUrl` AS `media_url`,`m`.`vMediaName` AS `media_name`,`m`.`vMediaFile` AS `media_file` FROM `user_media` AS `m` WHERE `m`.`iMediaId` IN ('4','5')
